{{ article_content }}

## Quality Standards
- Clarity and readability
- Completeness of information
- Proper markdown formatting
- Appropriate length and structure
- Accuracy of content
- Cross-reference opportunities

## Instructions
1. Evaluate the article against each quality standard
2. Identify specific issues or areas for improvement
3. Provide actionable recommendations
4. Suggest priority level for fixes

## Output Format
Provide audit results in JSON format:
{
  "score": 0-100,
  "issues": [
    {
      "type": "clarity|completeness|formatting|accuracy|structure",
      "severity": "low|medium|high",
      "description": "issue description",
      "recommendation": "how to fix"
    }
  ],
  "overall_feedback": "summary assessment"
}